question_stem: A study is performed to assess the efficacy of two new drugs for reducing systolic blood pressure in patients. There are three treatment groups - one used a placebo, while the other two groups used drug A and drug B. Study the SPSS output below. The interquartile range for treatment A group is [24626442-385a-4d77-a781-c826b2bcc44e] and for treatment B group is [62deb19c-5ec2-40b5-9a4e-c7b57b39fac7]. Give your answer to 2 decimal places.
